S3PhotoService class: Service for managing photography images in AWS S3

init: Initialize service with client and bucket configuration

test_connection: Test S3 bucket connection and accessibility

get_all_images: Retrieve all images from S3 originals folder with thumbnail generation

process_image_info: Process S3 object metadata and ensure thumbnail exists

check_thumbnail_exists: Verify if thumbnail image exists in S3 bucket

create_thumbnail: Generate and upload 300x300 thumbnail from original image

upload_image: Upload new image file to S3 originals folder with unique filename

is_image_file: Validate if S3 object is an image file by extension

root: API root endpoint with basic information

health_check: Health check endpoint to verify S3 connectivity

get_images: Fetch all portfolio images with thumbnails from S3